OL,3,CKeir Starmer blasts 'deeply
OL,4,Cconcerning' Kanye West festival
OL,5,Cheadline plans
OL,7,FThe rapper has drawn widespread
OL,8,Fcriticism in recent years after he
OL,9,Fbegan voicing admiration for Adolf
OL,10,FHitler, and has made a series of
OL,11,Fantisemitic remarks.
OL,13,FLast year, he released a song called
OL,14,F"Heil Hitler", only a few months after
OL,15,Fadvertising a Swastika T-shirt for
OL,16,Fsale on his website.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@MO]
