OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775383555
OL,3,CKeir Starmer blasts 'deeply
OL,4,Cconcerning' Kanye West festival
OL,5,Cheadline plans
OL,7,FAs first reported by The Sun on
OL,8,FSunday, Sir Keir said: "It is deeply
OL,9,Fconcerning that Kanye West has been
OL,10,Fbooked to perform at Wireless despite
OL,11,Fhis previous antisemitic remarks and
OL,12,Fcelebration of Nazism.
OL,14,F"Antisemitism in any form is abhorrent
OL,15,Fand must be confronted clearly and
OL,16,Ffirmly wherever it appears. Everyone
OL,17,Fhas a responsibility to ensure Britain
OL,18,Fis a place where Jewish people feel
OL,19,Fsafe and secure."
OL,26,@pD@XOUvD@AOU{D@QO]
