OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775383555
OL,3,CKeir Starmer blasts 'deeply
OL,4,Cconcerning' Kanye West festival
OL,5,Cheadline plans
OL,7,FIn October last year, two men were
OL,8,Fkilled in an attack on a Manchester
OL,9,Fsynagogue.
OL,11,FThe Sun on Sunday also published
OL,12,Fcriticism from a series of Jewish
OL,13,Fcommunity organisations which called
OL,14,Ffor Wireless Festival to think again
OL,15,Fabout allowing West to headline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
