OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775383555
OL,3,CKeir Starmer blasts 'deeply
OL,4,Cconcerning' Kanye West festival
OL,5,Cheadline plans
OL,7,FHolocaust Educational Trust boss,
OL,8,FKaren Pollock, told the newspaper the
OL,9,Fbooking was "causing distress to
OL,10,FBritain's Jewish community due to his
OL,11,Fprevious antisemitism and support for
OL,12,FHitler".
OL,14,FShe added: "Wireless should think
OL,15,Fagain about whether they want to
OL,16,Fprovide a platform for this hateful
OL,17,Fantisemitism."
OL,26,@qD@MOUtD@GO]vD@LOUyD@NO]
