OL,3,CKeir Starmer blasts 'deeply
OL,4,Cconcerning' Kanye West festival
OL,5,Cheadline plans
OL,7,FPhil Rosenberg, president of the Board
OL,8,Fof Deputies of British Jews, said it
OL,9,Fwas "absolutely the wrong decision" to
OL,10,Fallow West to play.
OL,12,FThe musician apologised in January for
OL,13,Fhis antisemitic remarks in a letter
OL,14,Fpublished as a full-page advert in the
OL,15,FWall Street Journal newspaper.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@cO]
