OL,3,CKeir Starmer blasts 'deeply
OL,4,Cconcerning' Kanye West festival
OL,5,Cheadline plans
OL,7,FIn his letter, he apologised to Jewish
OL,8,Fand black people, and said his bipolar
OL,9,Fdisorder led him to fall into "a four-
OL,10,Fmonth long, manic episode of
OL,11,Fpsychotic, paranoid and impulsive
OL,12,Fbehaviour that destroyed my life".
OL,14,FWireless Festival was contacted for
OL,15,Fcomment.
OL,26,@qD@_OUtD@aO]
